<html>
 <head>
  <title></title>
 </head>
 <body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 10px;" width="100%">
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <td align="center" bgcolor="#f6f6f6">
      <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff; width: 600px;">
       <tbody>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 0; background-color: #ffffff;"><img alt="AN-email-header" src="{[devName:ANemailheader]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="AN-email-header" /><a href="https://www.alliancenursing.com.au"> </a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;"><h1 style="font-size: 30px; line-height: 37px; color: #007DC3; font-weight: 900; font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Arial Black', Arial, sans-serif;">NSW HEALTH ONBOARDING.</h1> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;">To proceed with your application for [Job/Contract name], please complete the NSW Health onboarding documentation at your earliest convenvience.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Once completed, please return the signed documents to your Alliance Nursing team by replying to this email.&nbsp;</p> <p style="font-size:18px;line-height:25px;color:#000000; font-weight: 400; font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:10px 0 20px;"><a href="https://allianceaustralia.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/QE000002y78j/a/Oa000002aKGn/fli.aE3FFKCvAS8VVrzaGG.PtsWPDjR4wniFqXQcyEA">Employee personal details form</a><br /> <a href="https://allianceaustralia.my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/QE000002y78j/a/Oa000002aKLd/B1muruD.ry8TLb6LkwirmwjBfW..eI8vWA9o4PZmJOI">Onboarding information and checklist</a><br /> <br /> If you have any questions, you can always give&nbsp;us a call on&nbsp;<a href="tel:1300034494">1300 034 494</a>&nbsp;and speak to one of our consultants.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Kind regards,&nbsp;<br /> {{{Sender.FirstName}}}<br /> Alliance Nursing - Adelaide</p></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="height: 20px;">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 35px 0px 10px 0px;"><img alt="Alliance-graphic-line" src="{[devName:Alliancegraphicline]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="Alliance-graphic-line" /></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 26px 45px 40px 45px;font-size: 12px;line-height: 22px;color: #374250;">
          <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="/* margin: 0 auto; */">
           <tbody>
            <tr>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/alliancenursingaustralia"><img alt="fb-blue" src="{[devName:fbblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="fb-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/alliance-nursing-australia"><img alt="in-blue" src="{[devName:inblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="in-blue" /></a></td>
             <td style="padding-right: 16px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/alliancenursingaustralia/"><img alt="is-blue" src="{[devName:isblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="is-blue" /></a></td>
             <td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnMTM3MLQMFYj52ERo0E00Q"><img alt="yt-blue" src="{[devName:ytblue]}" style="max-width: 1623.55px" title="yt-blue" /></a></td>
            </tr>
           </tbody>
          </table></td>
        </tr>
       </tbody>
      </table></td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
 </body>
</html>